      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Don Cross</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b6/Don_cross.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Don_cross.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Don Cross <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Don Cross</b>,<br />\nan American software engineer, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Major_%28academic%29\">majored</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electrical_engineering\">electrical engineering</a> at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Central_Florida\">University of Central Florida</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe is author of the <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess program</a> <a href=\"/Chenard\" title=\"Chenard\">Chenard</a> and the open source <a href=\"/JavaScript\" title=\"JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> chess engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=Flywheel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Flywheel (page does not exist)\">Flywheel</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. His personal website covers various topics on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science\">science</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics\">mathematics</a>, <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">software</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronics\">electronics</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Postings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Postings</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Don_Cross&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Don Cross</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cosinekitty.com/raytrace/\">Fundamentals of Ray Tracing</a></i>. </li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Postings\">Postings</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Don_Cross&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Postings\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://levelup.gitconnected.com/create-your-own-expression-parser-d1f622077796\">Create Your Own Expression Parser  - Level Up Coding</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Don Cross</a>, February 01, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://levelup.gitconnected.com/build-your-own-chess-endgame-monster-a3fb23bb3ec1\">Build Your Own Chess Endgame Monster - Level Up Coding</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Don Cross</a>, February 17, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Don_Cross&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cosinekitty.com/\">Don Cross - personal website - math, science, software, electronics</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cosinekitty.com/arduino.html\">Arduino microcontroller projects</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Don Cross</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty\">cosinekitty (Don Cross) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty/chenard\">GitHub - cosinekitty/chenard: Chenard - a free chess program by Don Cross</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty/endgame\">GitHub - cosinekitty/endgame: Chess endgame database generator</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty/flywheel\">GitHub - cosinekitty/flywheel: A chess engine for the web browser</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Don_Cross&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty\">cosinekitty (Don Cross) · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://playground.arduino.cc/Profiles/CosineKitty\">Arduino Playground - CosineKitty</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cosinekitty/flywheel\">GitHub - cosinekitty/flywheel: A chess engine for the web browser</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://cosinekitty.com/\">Don Cross - personal website - math, science, software, electronics</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301154512\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6982-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301154511 and revision id 18447\n -->\n"
